room_title: Escape room "The Decoy" by The Escape Game Leavenworth in Leavenworth
room_description:
Many speakeasies in the 1920’s had fake businesses as cover operations for the illegal operations they were really running. Whether they looked like barber shops, blacksmith shops, delis or even medical practices, they were many times just masking the real business.
The “21” club has been successful thus far at masking the best speakeasy in the region and evading the feds. However, things are about to change...
